snippet.title: Mythmatch Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
Mythmatch is a community-building sim set in Greek Mythology. Match items to transform them. Match people to unite them. Rebuild Ithaca, create cute creatures, and defy the gods.

This is our debut trailer, which was shown at Wholesome Direct 2024.

Play the Demo on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1778050/Mythmatch/
Join our Discord: https://teamartichoke.com/discord
Website: https://www.teamartichoke.com/

Twitter: https://x.com/oneofmoo
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@oneofmoo
